            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a method for preparing porous ZnO/TiO2 hollow microspheres having a photocatalytic hydrogen production function. The method comprises the following steps: adding Ti(SO4)2, Zn(NO3)2.6H2O, NH4F and CO(NH2)2 into deionized water, and uniformly mixing the added substances and the deionized water to obtain a mixture A; stirring the mixture A for 60 min, placing the mixture A ina hydrothermal reaction kettle, heating the kettle to 180-220 DEG C for 10-15 h, and precipitating and filtering the obtained solution to obtain a sample B; and naturally cooling the sample B to roomtemperature, washing the cooled sample B, and drying the washed sample B at 60-80 DEG C for 8-12 h to obtain the porous ZnO/TiO2 hollow microspheres. The porous ZnO/TiO2 hollow microspheres prepared by adding the NH4F and CO(NH2)2 has a larger specific surface area than pure nano-particles, so the diffraction and the refraction of lights are facilitated, thereby the active sites and the light utilization rate of the above catalyst are increased. The catalyst has an excellent photocatalytic hydrogen production performance when applied to the field of new energy hydrogen production."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了种具有光催化制氢功能的多孔ZnO/TiO空心微米球的制备方法，将Ti(SO)和Zn(NO)·6HO，NHF，CO(NH)加入去离子水中混合均匀得到混合物A；将混合物A搅拌60分钟后放入水热反应釜中，在180‑220℃的条件下加热10‑15小时，经沉淀、过滤后得到样品B；将样品B自然冷却至室温，洗涤，60‑80℃干燥8‑12小时后得到多孔ZnO/TiO空心微米球。本发明通过添加NHF和CO(NH)制备多孔ZnO/TiO空心微米球，相对于单纯的纳米颗粒，该结构具有更大的比表面积，有利于光的衍射和折射，进而增加催化剂的活性位点和光的利率用。将该催化剂应用于新能源制氢领域，表现出优异的光催化产氢性能。"
                }
            ]
